data.description: Charming updated home offering the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and charm! Highlights include a newer roof, mini-split heating & air, and a detached garage with extra bonus space or even a possible 3rd bedroom. Enjoy the low maintenance landscaping ensuring minimal upkeep and fruit trees for your enjoyment! Beautiful paved walkways from the entrance for easy access to all of the property! Crown molding adds a touch of sophistication and detail to the interior. The kitchen is both functional and stylish, featuring a convenient breakfast bar. Step onto the inviting front porch, a perfect spot for relaxation!  The fenced and gated yard provides a secure and private space for outdoor activities! Plenty of extra space for boat or RV parking.
